 - Copy your Django project into this directory (or start a new one) as
 - Change settings at the top of fabfile.py
 - find . -type f | xargs perl -pi -e 's/foobar/yourproject/g'
 - change db password in fabfile and secret key in settings.py
 - change nginx config file name and doublecheck host within
 - generate new RSA keypair, put it in the server directory, upload the public key to github as your deploy key


